PLACEHOLDER: replace this file with the ASCII-armored public key produced by
the `gpg --armor --export <fingerprint>` step in docs/runbooks/backup-restore.md.

Until this file is replaced AND scripts/backup-recipient.fingerprint is
populated, the Ansible common role skips the keyring import and the nightly
backup.sh refuses to run. That is intentional — encrypting to no recipient
would silently produce un-decryptable files.
